memberdef.initializer: Class(const Class &) = delete;\ Class &operator=(const Class &) = delete;

detaileddescription.para: Copy/move deleters. Similar to Q_DISABLE_COPY_MOVE, et al. but those functions are not present in Qt < 5.13 so we use our own functions for portability.
